OL,3,CThis can't happen again: Call for
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry after smear test review
OL,6,FThere have been calls for a public
OL,7,Finquiry and for all Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fhealth trusts to re-examine the smear
OL,9,Ftests of thousands of women after
OL,10,Fcases were mis-read in two areas
OL,12,FOn Monday, County Armagh mum.
OL,14,FErin now has advanced-stage cervical
OL,15,Fcancer.
OL,17,FMany other women are still waiting to
OL,18,Ffind out if their tests were also mis-
OL,19,Fread.
