OL,3,CThis can't happen again: Call for
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry after smear test review
OL,6,FErin's case is understood to have
OL,7,Fprompted an audit by the Southern
OL,8,FTrust, leading to a major review of
OL,9,Fover 17,000 women's smear tests in the
OL,10,Farea.
OL,12,FTracey Bell and Heather Thompson spoke
OL,13,Fto UTV about how they are still
OL,14,Fwaiting on the outcome of their smear
OL,15,Ftest review.
OL,17,FThey're calling for a public inquiry
OL,18,Finto all five health trusts, fearing
OL,19,Fthat the cases found in the Southern
OL,20,Fand Western Trust areas may not be the
OL,21,Ffull picture.
