OL,3,CThis can't happen again: Call for
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry after smear test review
OL,6,FTracey Bell told UTV: "That's what
OL,7,Fit's going to take to get everything
OL,8,Fout in the open and that women then
OL,9,Fhave confidence going forward.
OL,11,FHeather Thompson added: "This can
OL,12,Fnever happen again... over 17,500
OL,13,Fladies over a 13-year period have been
OL,14,Finformed that they've had to have
OL,15,Ftheir test rechecked."
OL,17,F"We really want to know who is
OL,18,Fresponsible," said Tracey.
