OL,4,Cpublic inquiry after smear test review
OL,6,FThe women also want to know if those
OL,7,Fwho misread the smear tests are still
OL,8,Fworking.
OL,10,FSDLP MLA Colin McGrath is on
OL,11,FStormont's Health Committee and has
OL,12,Fbacked an independent inquiry into all
OL,13,FHealth Trusts.
