OL,3,CThis can't happen again: Call for
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry after smear test review
OL,6,FUlster University Professor Deirdre
OL,7,FHeenan said: "Women are being failed
OL,8,Fand of course, if you can't trust a
OL,9,Fscreening process then women will
OL,10,Fthink twice about taking their next
OL,11,Fappointment and it's hugely important
OL,12,Fthat they don't, that we say to women
OL,13,Fthat you must have trust and
OL,14,Fconfidence in the system.
OL,16,F"But if this is not rectified and
OL,17,Frectified quickly, the knock-on
OL,18,Faffects would be hard to overstate."
OL,20,FBoth the Southern and Western Health
OL,21,FTrusts have apologised.
